28 SECTION 2, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
29 JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 7. (a) A valuable metal dealer who fails to comply
30 with this chapter commits a Class A infraction. In addition, the
31 valuable metal dealer may be subject to a criminal penalty under
32 IC 35-43-4-3.3.
33 (b) A valuable metal dealer who:
34 (1) knowingly or intentionally fails to comply with this chapter;
35 and
36 (2) purchases stolen valuable metal;
37 commits concealing a valuable metal purchase, a Level 6 felony.
