39 SECTION 1, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
40 JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 1. If a person has an unpaid claim on a liability
41 that is covered by IC 24-4.6-5 or suffers a pecuniary loss as a result of
42 a violation of IC 25-37.5, IC 35-43, IC 35-42-3-3, IC 35-42-3-4,
